{"tid":1372640,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係香港人！","createTime":"2019-07-27T13:10:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T13:10:48.000Z","uid":137285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4b6263a681815c69c97567f0093716b43eeb2bca","tid":1372640,"uid":137285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T13:10:48.000Z","msg":"啱啱係屋企同咗藍絲犬隻嘈交<br />\n我話我唔認自己係終國人<br />\n我話我係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">港</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">人</span></strong></span> ！<br />\n因為我唔會承認一個殺人政權 一個唔願對歷史認錯既極權統治國家<br />\n佢話終國如果認咗錯就會受國際更強既制裁 仲話日本都無承認過當年侵華殺人既錯誤 同終國一樣改歷史 但就無人去話日本<br />\n跟住就比其他藍絲屋企人指住黎屌<br />\n唔想同佢地嘈就入咗房<br />\n<br />\n嬲撚到癲"}]}